# Epic 1: Foundational Setup & Core User Authentication

## Problem Analysis

- **Goal**: Establish the initial project structure, database schema for users, implement user authentication for the initial admin (with "First Run" experience), secure application access via middleware, and implement client-side session validation.
- **Key Requirements**:
  - Scaffold folder structure based on project context
  - Initialize Next.js project with all required tooling
  - Integrate Prisma ORM with SQLite and define User schema
  - Implement NextAuth.js authentication with name/password support
  - Create API endpoint for user tiles
  - Develop tile-based login page UI
  - Implement "First Run" experience for initial admin setup
  - Secure routes with middleware and client-side validation

